Executive Profile
W. Bradford Hu  Chief Risk Officer, Citigroup Inc.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 1 Board Members in 1 different organizations across 5 different industries.See Board Relationships54--
Background

		Mr. W. Bradford Hu, also known as Brad, has been the Chief Risk Officer of Citigroup, Inc. since January 7, 2013. Mr. Hu served as the Head of Risk for Asia Pacific Region at Citigroup, Inc. until January 7, 2013. He served as Managing Director of Wells Fargo Advisors, LLC since July 2005. He joined Wachovia Securities from Morgan Stanley, where he served as the Head of Global Capital Markets in Japan at Morgan Stanley until April 2008. He held a variety of positions ... within both Corporate Finance and Equity Capital Markets and focused on Financial Sponsors and Financial Institutions Groups. He has been Non Executive Director of Citigroup Korea Inc. since 2010. He served as a Non Executive Director of Citibank Korea Inc. since 2010. Mr. Hu holds a B.S. and an M.S. degree in electrical engineering & Computer Science from the Massachusetts Institute of Technology and an M.B.A. from the Amos Tuck School of Business Administration at Dartmouth College.Read Full Background




